{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 2070667, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "piraka810", "body": "[quote][i][b]And that's... one hundred...[/b][/i][/quote]", "date": "2014-12-16T20:44:17-06:00", "rating": 93, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "We DID owe him one.", "creationdate": "2014-12-16T23:02:11-06:00", "id": 814230, "rating": 31, "commentid": 2070667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ProjectSixam", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I actually love what they did there. How many people forgot about the last one, I wonder?", "creationdate": "2014-12-18T09:02:52-06:00", "id": 814954, "rating": 10, "commentid": 2070667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bunnyslippers12", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Madbag, Kargath saying \"And that's... one hundred...\" is in reference to him saying he only counted ninety-nine kills in Tanaan Jungle, OUR kills. Also, he IS an ally/friend of the Ogres, because the Ogres allied with the Iron Horde.", "creationdate": "2014-12-18T17:18:24-06:00", "id": 815151, "rating": 7, "commentid": 2070667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "blacknexus94", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "But isn't it actually more than a hundred? Since we killed a whole bunch more of his guys in between escaping that arena and fighting him to the death?", "creationdate": "2014-12-18T23:31:35-06:00", "id": 815273, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2070667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "JStryker47", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "@JStryker47: They were not inside the arena, that's why", "creationdate": "2014-12-30T02:37:41-06:00", "id": 820684, "rating": 8, "commentid": 2070667, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Whoisthiscook", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 2072802, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Warchief1223", "body": "In BC he looked like a giant red boar monster\r\nIn WoD he looks like an orcish Nathan Explosion.", "date": "2014-12-20T05:50:28-06:00", "rating": 53, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 2074905, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Faerdin", "body": "[quote]Kargath Bladefist yells: I am pleased. I could watch you rats fight for hours.\r\nArchmage Khadgar says: Sorry, but we don't have that kind of time.[/quote]\r\n\r\n[i]Later that day...[/i]\r\n\r\nKargath: What about now?\r\nKhadgar: Sorry. Bonus objectives.\r\n\r\n[i]Later that week...[/i]\r\n\r\nKargath: Now?\r\nKhadgar: Apexis dailies.\r\n\r\n[i]Later that month...[/i]\r\n\r\nKargath: Now?\r\nKhadgar: I'm filling the work orders on my barn!\r\n\r\n[i]Highmaul Release[/i]\r\n\r\nKargath: Now?\r\nKhadgar: Okay. 10-25 people are going to gang up on you and faceroll until you die at your earliest convenience.\r\nKargath: Sounds good.\r\n\r\n[b]Combatants slain in the arena (100)[/b]", "date": "2014-12-23T06:58:52-06:00", "rating": 82, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It would have been a pretty neat plot line if not for the fact that he's the first raid boss of the expansion and dies if you so much as look at him. All that build up for a fight that a dozen poorly trained monkeys could win.", "creationdate": "2015-01-22T09:43:45-06:00", "id": 831217, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2074905, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "defektunge", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Glad to hear you are a poorly trained monkey.", "creationdate": "2015-06-19T00:27:39-05:00", "id": 876295, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2074905, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "illwit", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
