{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 2084044, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Lightbrand", "body": "Imagine an adventurer's journey in his life so far in Azeroth.\n\nClassic:  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=17182]Sulfuras[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19019]Thunderfury[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22691]Corrupted Ashbringer[/url] & [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22589]Atiesh[/url].\n\nTBC:  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=29348]The Bladefist[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28773]Gorehowl[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/itemset=699]Warglaives[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32483]Skull of Gul'dan[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=34334]Thori'dal[/url].  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=16524]Shade of Aran[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=22589]Atiesh[/url].\n\nWrath:  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=46017]Val'anyr[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=49623]Shadowmourne[/url].  [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=36597]Arthas[/url] dies to retconned [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=13262]Ashbringer[/url] :(\n\nCata: Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=46753]Al'akir[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19019]Thunderfury[/url],  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=52409]Ragnaros[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=17182]Sulfuras[/url], Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=71086]Dragonwrath[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/itemset=1087]Fangs of the Father[/url],  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=56173]Deathwing[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/itemset=1087]Fangs[/url] (though he technically died to Dragon Soul).\n\nMist: Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/items=4?filter=qu=5;ty=-6:-5:-7:6:-8:0;minle=600]Legendary Cape[/url], defeat [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=71865]Garrosh[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28773]Gorehowl[/url], obtain [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112935/tusks-of-mannoroth]Tusk of Mannaroth[/url], optionally picks up [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112925]Xal'atoh[/url].\n\nWarlords:  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=76407]Ner'zul[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=49623]Shadowmourne[/url].  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=78714]Kargath[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=29348]The Bladefist[/url], get [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=113591]another pair[/url].  Kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=77325]Blackhand[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=113979]The Black Hand[/url].  [s]Smash Gul'dan with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=32483]Skull of Gul'dan[/url][/s].  Acquire [url=http://www.wowhead.com/items=4?filter=minle=600;qu=5;ty=-2]Legendary Ring[/url],  [s]and Ultimately kill Grommash with either [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=28773]Gorehowl[/url] again or if you're twisted, his son's [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112925]Xal'atoh[/url].[/s] Ram [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=91349/mannoroth]Mannaroth[/url] with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=112935/tusks-of-mannoroth]Tusk of Mannaroth[/url].\n\nTo some, our adventurer's actions may sound like poetry to the ears, to some it's borderline creepy.   But as a bonus story, what if I told you on the first visit to [url=http://www.wowhead.com/zone=5094]Blackwing Descent[/url], our favorite adventurer bared an eerie grin throughout the raid...because inside the trusty backpack lied [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19003]two[/url][url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=18422] heads[/url] that failed to make it to the capital all these years...", "date": "2015-01-07T03:26:11-06:00", "rating": 41, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Aha thanks for this little jewel you shared with us! Hard part btw is to get the Tusk of Mannoroth, i know people with more than 500 tries on Garrosh withouth luck.", "creationdate": "2016-04-01T03:32:54-05:00", "id": 936459, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2084044, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "wisedada", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2015-07-21T22:36:31-05:00", 14, "Lightbrand"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 2101020, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "AliceInAcidland", "body": "Imperator Mar'gok yells:\r\nYou honor us, Kargath. I will enjoy watching you fight in the arena again, even with your...\r\n\r\n\u00a0\u00a0/\\\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u220f\r\n(\u2022_\u2022) (  [u]\u2022[/u]  )\r\n\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0/\\\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u220f\r\n( \u2022_\u2022)>\u2310\u25a0-\u25a0 (  [u]\u2022[/u]  )>\u2310\u25a0\r\n\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0/\\ \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u220f\r\n(\u2310\u25a0_\u25a0)( \u2310[u]\u25a0[/u]  )\r\n\r\nHandicap.", "date": "2015-02-08T07:23:12-06:00", "rating": 69, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "\"The pleasure is mine! The crowd deserves a surperior gladiator, seeing as the last one fell so easily.", "creationdate": "2018-12-07T03:17:30-06:00", "id": 1207960, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2101020, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "SilverDragon234", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
