{"commentv2": 1, "number": 51, "id": 1917368, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Gotnov", "body": "Wonder if this guy will be a boss in Warlords of Draenor.  Will be kind of weird if he's stronger there, since he is older and more experienced in BC compared to the time of WoD.  But he will be stronger in WoD I guess,  gameplay > sense.", "date": "2013-11-11T23:34:11-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Levels are not a proper judge of character strength. A kobold in Northrend is not actually more powerful than VanCleef, for example.", "creationdate": "2013-11-13T13:55:03-06:00", "id": 707836, "rating": 14, "commentid": 1917368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It would \"Make sense\", considering they've already said it's an alternate timeline, so anything goes really. All the characters there are going to be a lot stronger than they were in BC since it will be level 100 content. :P", "creationdate": "2014-01-25T13:37:31-06:00", "id": 724233, "rating": -3, "commentid": 1917368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "PuppyToast", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Wasn't it stated that Garrosh plan is to go to an alternate Draenor to gather a new \"True Horde\" by equipping legends of the past with the equipment and technology of today? Or something along those lines. Even if that doesnt work, we can always go with the \"Well, its because his mind is really sharp because he isnt possessed by warlocky magic.\"", "creationdate": "2014-04-07T13:26:05-05:00", "id": 739230, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1917368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Chaoslux", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "\"A kobold in Northrend is not actually more powerful than VanCleef, for example\". Or is it? =)", "creationdate": "2014-08-14T14:15:25-05:00", "id": 764713, "rating": -5, "commentid": 1917368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Xaruman", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 52, "id": 1946972, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Zoeteklem", "body": "[b]Updated info for this NPC as of 5.4.2 from [url=http://us.battle.net/wow/en/warlords-of-draenor/#characters]here[/url]:[/b]\r\n\r\nIn the new Warlords of Draenor expansion, [npc=16808] was described as:\r\n\r\n[quote]\"Kargath Bladefist leads an army of sadists simply by being the most hate-filled orc to ever attach a scythe to the stump of his severed wrist. Initiates of Kargath\u2019s clan, the Shattered Hand, emulate their chieftain\u2019s vicious body modification, but it\u2019s only the first of many opportunities for new scars, both on their own bodies and in the sculpting clay of their foes\u2019 flesh.\"[/quote]", "date": "2014-02-26T17:21:04-06:00", "rating": 13, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 53, "id": 1967752, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Durantye", "body": "Has been confirmed that Kargath will be a raid boss in Warlords of Draenor, you can look at his early Dungeon Journal describing the fight on MMO-Champion. It seems to be a Gladiatorial type fight where you have to gave favor to gain a buff to defeat Kargath. Likely by eliminating those in the stands that disagree with your fighting tactics/how ever the crowd judges you.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.mmo-champion.com/threads/1522642-Warlords-of-Draenor-Alpha-Build-18297-Encounter-Journals?p=27209224#post27209224", "date": "2014-05-25T16:07:37-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
