{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2000075, "nreplies": 6, "sticky": 0, "user": "bossfight1", "body": "From the footage I've seen\u2014namely [url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KpzfmKTZp8U]Fatboss's[/url] video\u2014Kargath doesn't die at the end of this fight. His bladefist is severed from his wrist, and he flees from the arena just as Cho'gall arrives to cause some havoc. Guess we'll be seeing more of him down the line.", "date": "2014-09-06T16:17:12-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "They changed it. He dies now sadly.", "creationdate": "2014-09-15T06:50:50-05:00", "id": 772132, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2000075, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Draintwo", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Damn. Kargath's my favorite orc. Really sad he only gets a few screams and gets instantly taken down. I wanted more of him...", "creationdate": "2014-10-01T15:03:21-05:00", "id": 776083, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2000075, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Galhaar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Unfortunately, I just killed him twice today (first on Heroic, then on Normal) and he most certainly dies when defeated. I agree that it's a bit of a waste.", "creationdate": "2014-12-03T16:33:37-06:00", "id": 805765, "rating": 5, "commentid": 2000075, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ashiraya", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He does actually die as seen here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Q3GN6-9_qs. I actually take that as a good sign in that maybe Blizzard are going to decrease their expansion cycles and decided to kill him so that they do not need him for more content.", "creationdate": "2014-12-05T14:10:48-06:00", "id": 807105, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2000075, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "xerty", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Yep, he dies now. I kinda liked the sense of foreboding from watching him haul ass out of the arena once we beat him, but his death line \"And that's... one hundred.\" makes up for it.", "creationdate": "2014-12-08T22:49:28-06:00", "id": 809476, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2000075, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "bossfight1", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
