{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 2021649, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "Slaskvatten", "body": "I personally think that this is just a disgrace. Kargath Bladefist, warchief of the shattered hand, by far the most awesome warlord, dies, once again, in the start of the f-ing expansion. Please blizz, give him what he deserves, the most badass fight ever seen, in any game, movie or whatever, that you can possibly make.", "date": "2014-10-31T17:34:54-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He is just a dude who went through a lot of shit. He is a badass at gladiator stuff against people who are fighting with little to shit but we aren't fighting with a broken sword.", "creationdate": "2014-11-07T23:06:30-06:00", "id": 787065, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2021649, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Deviousmist", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He wont die, when you defeat him he will escape. And we will probably fight him in the future.", "creationdate": "2014-11-10T12:00:32-06:00", "id": 787810, "rating": 13, "commentid": 2021649, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "leonmarkes", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Imho (I dont know the ending of the Blackhand fight), escape will be the case of many warlords which we face this early in the expansion (or important lore figures for that matter - think Terongor) and would be such a shame to waste Kargath and his potential so early. That goes for Blackhand too, but he is end boss anyway so...I could live with that..", "creationdate": "2014-11-20T15:34:12-06:00", "id": 794953, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2021649, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "xdrumtardikx", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I don't know what you guys are talking about, it doesnt matter if it's kargath or blackhand the first warlord to die, there must be a first one, as long as it's not either Grom or Gul'dan. And by the way, the ACTUAL disgrace is Ner'zhul being a shitty dungeon boss, I believe Blizzard will still put him back though, since he controls the dead", "creationdate": "2014-11-28T22:25:04-06:00", "id": 802121, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2021649, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Artharys", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Ans yet... he dies... such a pity.", "creationdate": "2014-12-03T19:06:44-06:00", "id": 805870, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2021649, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "omaox", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 2024073, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Keasha", "body": "Summary of the fight:\r\n\r\n- Do not stand in the bad stuff (fire pillars, patches on the ground, etc.)\r\n- Do not fall into the pits\r\n- Taunt boss after some amount of impale stacks\r\n- Stand spread to prevent additional damage from blade dance\r\n- Kite Kargath through his berserker rush\r\n- Get your best dps, the current tank and one healer near Kargath before Chain Hurl to kill the adds on arena's stands\r\n\r\nIn Mythic:\r\n- Kite kitties into fire pillars to stack the dps buff\r\n- Kill kitties before the next one spawns\r\n- Do everything to stack the dps buff and prevent everything to lose the dps buff", "date": "2014-11-04T02:29:34-06:00", "rating": 19, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "you kite kargath into the fire pillars during his berserker rush, it interrupts it and he smashes the pillar", "creationdate": "2014-12-06T23:26:16-06:00", "id": 808070, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2024073, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Tenjen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 2039270, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "EnderDragon", "body": "I find it funny that Kargath (well, Blizzard really) is not sure what hand he is missing. His in-game model has him missing his left hand, but the loading screen has him missing his right hand.", "date": "2014-11-18T22:48:17-06:00", "rating": 34, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "came here to say that...", "creationdate": "2014-11-20T15:28:27-06:00", "id": 794947, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2039270, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "xdrumtardikx", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "in the movie it was his left so that one is probably cannon the one in the loading screen is most likely flipped for ascetics", "creationdate": "2014-12-01T20:55:09-06:00", "id": 804430, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2039270, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "vindurza", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "For your insight, this is a common problem among Graphic Designers, they mirror the image after creation. It is a common Task, dont ask me why. So in general he has designed the image correct, but after the mirror the false hand is off. Sry for the bad english", "creationdate": "2014-12-01T23:52:53-06:00", "id": 804539, "rating": 5, "commentid": 2039270, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "raensen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "We know one thing for sure: In the end, he will be missing both ;)", "creationdate": "2014-12-10T14:06:13-06:00", "id": 810478, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2039270, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Elosha", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I don't have the link anymore but I distinctly remember a blue post or tweet where they mentioned he used to be on the right but they flipped the image for composition.", "creationdate": "2015-01-13T19:41:15-06:00", "id": 827596, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2039270, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Mormolyce", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
