{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 2058311, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "spollo", "body": "This fight is one of the most badass I've experienced in a long time. You feel less like a powerful hero, and more like a mook.\nHe grabs your tank and [i]runs him through[/i] on that blade of his, taunts him to his face, and then throws him back down to the ground. It's brutal. Also, hard on healers.\nOccasionally he will run towards a ranged dps, screaming deliriously while swinging his bladefist out in front of him, mowing your dudes down like old, squishy bananas. The final kicker - he throws chains around members of the raid, then [i]twirls the raid members over his head and hurls them into the grandstands.[/i] It has to be seen. \n\nEven though the fight is mechanically pretty easy on normal mode, I still feel like I got my ass kicked.", "date": "2014-12-03T21:46:36-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2014-12-03T21:50:06-06:00", 4, "spollo"]}
